videos.description: Clemson RB Travis Etienne converts at the goal line, powering through the defense and diving into the end zone for a three-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Etienne lunges into end zone) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Etienne lunges into end zone

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence throws a quick pass to Diondre Overton, who weaves through the defense for a 22-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Lawrence tosses TD to Overton) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Lawrence tosses TD to Overton

videos.description: AJ Dillon runs up the gut for a nine-yard touchdown, giving Boston College its first points of the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Dillon puts BC on the board) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Dillon puts BC on the board

videos.description: Clemson RB Travis Etienne takes a pitch and spins into the end zone for his second touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Etienne finds pay dirt for 2nd time) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Etienne finds pay dirt for 2nd time

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence tosses a screen pass to Amari Rodgers, who jukes past a defender and goes 19 yards untouched for a Clemson score.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Rodgers puts a move on defense, scores Clemson TD) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Rodgers puts a move on defense, scores Clemson TD

videos.description: Travis Etienne racks up his third rushing touchdown of the game, scoring from five yards out to give Clemson a 38-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Etienne's 3rd TD puts Clemson up big) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Etienne's 3rd TD puts Clemson up big

videos.description: Clemson LB Chad Smith gets the strip sack on Boston College QB Dennis Grosel and Logan Rudolph returns the fumble to the house for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Clemson defense gets scoop-and-score TD) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Clemson defense gets scoop-and-score TD

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence rolls to his left and throws a perfect pass to Diondre Overton for a 63-yard Clemson touchdown.

videos.headline: Lawrence drops dime to Overton for TD
